Text: RE Tibco implementation at DealBenchThanks a lot Harry Sharma Original Message From Arora Harry mailtoHarry NRONcom Sent Tuesday February PM To Cc Raghavan Suresh Subject Tibco implementation at DealBench Sharma We have completed our first year at DealBench It has been an exciting and fruitful year when we launched our platform and evolved the business I wanted to take a moment to appreciate your help in making this a success You help was critical in getting our implementation done in a reasonable time frame Also I appreciate your help in teaching Tibco products to other outside consultants who worked with us Please feel free in sharing this email with your supervisor or others in your company Ecommerce implementations are hard business and there is always a time crunch and we appreciate your hard work and extra effort in making this business implementation possible in a timely fashion Thanks Harry Arora Vice President Enron NetWorks
